    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riot Ride 是一款 <strong>街机汽车战斗</strong> 游戏，拥有 <strong>roguelike</strong> 机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶一辆<strong>武装汽车</strong>，在 <strong>程序生成的</strong> 关卡中探索 <strong>复古</strong> 和 <strong>类似 Tron</strong> 的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集 <strong>蓝图</strong> 并安全送回，同时抵御 <strong>各种盗版车辆</strong> 的攻击，防止它们终结你的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/b76e271eb41799b18fbb4995d5f37830.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限的游戏风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店里寻找 <strong>武器</strong> 和购买 <strong>被动物品</strong> 以求生存。利用这些物品 <strong>无限定制</strong> 你的汽车，并 <strong>进一步个性化你的游戏风格</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/a8b1bdfed7e07866b79429c096bd527d.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性的Boss</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对 <strong>越来越困难的Boss</strong>，每个Boss都有 <strong>独特的攻击模式</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/cdcad9b6436f781bf5ad58a914486682.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >永久死亡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩、死、学习和重复</strong>，直到你面对<strong>最终恶棍</strong>，在残酷的对决中最终突破模拟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.poster.avif?t=1736094031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.webm?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/80de2a4b007b7b1534469e2ab8ef839f.mp4?t=1736094031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可玩36个关卡 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多达17种独特武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与8种独特敌人作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对9个Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果死亡，则丧失所有进度</p></li></ul>",
